---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Terminal Scope">
    <div class="animate-fade-in max-w-2xl mx-auto">
       <div class="bg-surface p-1 rounded-t-md flex items-center gap-2 px-3">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-error"></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-accent"></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-success"></div>
          <span class="ml-2 text-xs opacity-50 font-mono">vim ~/about.md</span>
       </div>
       <div class="border-x border-b p-6 font-mono text-sm leading-loose whitespace-pre-wrap border-surface">
{`# About the Creator

# Welcome to Terminal Scope

My name is Jordan and I created this website to serve as a place I can save and share content and ideas I find interesting. I've created this site in the theme of TUI or Terminal User Interface off of my inspirations of sci-fi user interfaces.

# Tech Stack

-  **Framework**: Astro 5.16.0

-  **UI Framework**: React 19.2.0 (for interactive components)

-  **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 3.4.18 with custom theme

-  **Content**: Markdown/MDX with Astro Content Collections

-  **Deployment**: GitHub Pages (static hosting)

## Contact
GitHub: @redunix`}
         <span class="inline-block w-2 h-4 bg-accent animate-pulse align-middle ml-1"></span>
       </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
